                "invention-title": [
                    "Crystallization and separation process for byproduct sodium bromide generated after oxidation of brominated hydrocarbon waste gas",
                    "一种溴代烃废气氧化后副产物溴化钠结晶分离工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a crystallization and separation process of a byproduct sodium bromide after oxidation of brominated hydrocarbon waste gas, and belongs to the technical field of waste gas treatment. In the reaction process, a sodium carbonate solution is adopted to replace a sodium hydroxide solution for hydrogen bromide absorption, so that the purity of a precipitated crystal sodium bromide product is improved, and sodium carbonate crystals cannot be retained in a system to cause blockage of system equipment and pipelines; according to the invention, salt crystals in the concentrated salt pond are filtered out by adopting the simple plate-and-frame filter press, so that the investment cost is saved; waste heat generated by the RTO incinerator is used for evaporating, dewatering and concentrating absorption liquid, compressed air is heated, salt crystals obtained through filter pressing are subjected to high-temperature purging and drying, the sodium bromide product with the small water content is obtained, no additional heat source is needed for drying the product, and energy conservation and consumption reduction are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种溴代烃废气氧化后副产物溴化钠结晶分离工艺，属于废气处理技术领域。本发明在反应流程中采用碳酸钠溶液代替氢氧化钠溶液进行溴化氢吸收，提高了析出晶体溴化钠产品的纯度，且碳酸钠晶体不会滞留在系统里，造成系统设备、管道堵塞；本发明采用简单板框压滤机压滤出浓盐池里的盐晶体，节省了投资成本；本发明用RTO焚烧炉产生的余热对吸收液进行蒸发除水提浓，以及对压缩空气进行加热，对压滤出来的盐晶体进行高温吹扫干燥，得到含水量小的溴化钠产品，不需要另外的热源干燥产品，节能降耗。"
                }
            ]
